	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A nice little trick to killing trumpy if you're a caster...<BR>
<BR>
Wait in the alley between Fish's Ale and Voleen's Baked Goods (or something like that).  Trumpy will eventually wander out to the docks and start harassing the fisherman out there.  You have two chances to get his attention, once going and once coming.<BR>
<BR>
When you see him going out to the docks (he'll walk right in front of you if you're looking to the water), or returning from the docks if you missed him the first time, hit him with a direct damage or DoT spell.  He'll come running right to you without his buddies.  I got him with two castings of Spirit Strike (75 points each).<BR>
<BR>
The only thing to watch out for are the Corrupt Guards that patrol through this alley.  If you time it right, you can get Trumpy without a scratch (no scrathes on my L15 Shaman anyway).
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
